      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution' id='S6CV0385P0-04037'>
        <a name='S6CV0385P0_20020514_WH_45'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/mr-julian-brazier' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S6CV0385P0_20020514_WH_45' title='Link to this speech by Mr Julian Brazier' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
